article_id:3039,category_name:Events,title_name:A New Raid Event, Advent of the Origin, Is Coming Soon!,image_path:https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/54a8a69f64b193ac3aed25fb16b98ca9.png,message:<div>The Advent of the Origin raid event begins on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1648620000"></span>. During this event, you can use co-op play to fight against a raid boss with no elemental attunement.<br><br></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/54a8a69f64b193ac3aed25fb16b98ca9.png"></div><div>This event&#39;s theme song is &quot;Destiny&quot; by Hitomi Miyahara and Honoka Watanabe.</div><div><br></div><div>■Event Duration<br><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1648620000"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1650002399"></span></div><div><br>■Notes<br>1. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 / 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign to participate in event quests.<br>2. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 / 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign to play co-op.<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1648360800,update_time1647418779